{"tid":1112521,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"馬場站個廁所可以話係成條東鐵個清泉","createTime":"2019-04-17T12:20:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T13:15:27.000Z","uid":123613,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b4081f942b46b800672e2b33a84f4f8b447236","tid":1112521,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:20:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日要搭東鐵，東鐵多蝗是常識吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n頭先撞正跑馬，咁啱搭中經馬場站班車，馬場站一星期先開兩日，兩日仲要開得幾個鐘，個廁所肯定唔會好似東鐵其他站一樣烏煙瘴氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身個肚少少唔舒服，一去到馬場站，就算下一班車要等成15-20分鐘，頭也不回地去住先，喺東鐵唯一咁乾淨個屎塔暢快地痾屎，簡直係享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有時間打個丁先搭下班車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"000bb9956ee8d554763df793e752a2ad8eb9021b","tid":1112521,"uid":123613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0661b3dd4fc966cc0e71baba24c21b32e34c805f","tid":1112521,"uid":145235,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T12:42:01.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"820d4e0f9ae7d6ac8b626d9e97892e26d47cbe11","tid":1112521,"uid":208817,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"本身或者清泉嘅 你打完丁就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14820c4036353ec6c863b749bc25840cc7fd5f59","tid":1112521,"uid":164920,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:00:57.000Z","msg":"大把賭馬阿叔用過既廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7361fe823991bd405007d3c64f4c87a36a0c687","tid":1112521,"uid":51720,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T13:04:48.000Z","msg":"馬場站只係得月